{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6fdd6a4759","title":"毛泽东在听取钱信忠、张凯汇报卫生工作时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2086f209cc","index":0,"year":1965,"month":8,"day":2,"articleId":"6fdd6a4759"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8c2fdb2068","type":"title","text":"在听取钱信忠、张凯汇报卫生工作时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"ad415e2d0e","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"69f32cfbed","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我要讲的都讲了。你们打算怎么办？","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"d68605f082","type":"paragraph","text":"答：（略。汇报到打算为农村生产队培训不脱产卫生员）","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"947a5bc148","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：训练多长时间？","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"4ef137fe4f","type":"paragraph","text":"答：半个月左右。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"220f12044a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：半个月太短了吧！","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"9b7aa4b32f","type":"paragraph","text":"答：他们主要学会些针灸，常见病的治疗和一些预防工作，训练后还要带他们做。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"347b5bee50","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：带很重要，带多长时间？","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"88744f9247","type":"paragraph","text":"答：城市医疗队下去可一直带，共带三、四个月。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"d0e63ee80c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这还可以，带三、四个月，学会治十几种病。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"b5b08ba81a","type":"paragraph","text":"（当汇报到搞了一些半农半读训练班时。）","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"d3cedf89d3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：半农半读怎么搞法？","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"de30d42537","type":"paragraph","text":"答：采取农忙不学，农闲多学的方式。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"2e1d415632","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：多长时间？","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"4076e37849","type":"paragraph","text":"答：两年，三年。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"c64250f312","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：两年就是读一年书，三年就是读一年半书，这个办法好。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"ba166c25ca","type":"paragraph","text":"（当汇报到根据毛的指示卫生部作了检查时。）","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"405fb6c342","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：现在有多少卫生技术人员？","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"bafc0f22b1","type":"paragraph","text":"答：（略）","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"561e6e22ba","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这个队伍不小！","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"a9d010fed9","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：主席批评我们只为城市人口服务，很对。现在高级医务人员百分之八十在城市，其中百分之七十在大城市，百分之二十在县城，只有百分之十在农村。经费，包括县在内，农村占百分之二十五，百分之七十五用在城市。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"33505a0fdf","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们用了这么多人力、这么多钱，为那么少的人服务。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"d224fe99de","type":"paragraph","text":"答：主席指示后，才清醒了。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"de90a783ec","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们研究过神医没有？","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"9c1f45f531","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我们没有研究过。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"bde615784c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：神医有个好处：神药它保险，不会害人，没有毒；第二个好处是省钱，几个铜板就可以了；第三是给病人精神安慰，病也就好了。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"2775f4326f","type":"paragraph","text":"答：许多病不治也可以好。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"4b002a6b6f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：比骗人的医生要好。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"d005cbaae4","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：通过四清和医疗队下乡，了解到农村卫生队伍很复杂。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"7a56ecdeda","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：怎么复杂？","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"83445be0c0","type":"paragraph","text":"答：有许多人过去不是医生，看些医书就加入到医务人员队伍里来了。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"c5a9aa120e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：看些什么书？","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"f319ce7500","type":"paragraph","text":"答：看些中医书，看些药方。农村医务队伍中，政治情况复杂，技术水平低的占百分之四十左右。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"cc79fe335a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：坏人不多吧？","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"e089ad2744","type":"paragraph","text":"答：真正坏人占百分之五左右，但政治技术水平低的较多，占百分之四十左右，这个队伍如果没有新生力量，取消他们还不容易。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"695fde4797","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：现在正在召开医学教育会议，讨论主席、总理指示，要办三年制卫生学校，为农村培养医生。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"baba98fd87","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：高等教育要五年，读那么长时间书，值得研究。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"648d732a6c","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：现在想两条腿走路，办三年制，多在农村办，在农村招生。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"65f3c5d326","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：招什么生？","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"345a78afd8","type":"paragraph","text":"答：大部分招高中生。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"7d53d38527","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：初中生还不行吗？","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"7496a70d3d","type":"paragraph","text":"答：目前农村高中生还不少。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"369165d15c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：招中学生还不行吗？你们不在城市招了吗？","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"5eeb9537a9","type":"paragraph","text":"答：城市也招一些，主要在农村招。","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"8a233c0b3a","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到医生政治思想最重要，只有技术没有政治不行时）","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"bd89436f0a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这一点很重要。医生一定要政治好，招些政治好的中学生就可以了。","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"be234267aa","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报到城市问题时。","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"c11bb1bddb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们对城市是不是服务得好？","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"8810fd3607","type":"paragraph","text":"答：也没有服务好，要求愈来愈高。","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"cfd6d07e3a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：怎么愈来愈高？","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"9e508a7dda","type":"paragraph","text":"答：以北京来讲，××多万干部公费医疗，××多万工人劳保，还有家属。","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"104c1dccd5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：工人不是“老爷”，工人还是要为他们服务的。","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"0a242a0409","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：工厂医务工作没有搞好，工人也都到医院去看病。","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"0eeaea871c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们为什么不在工厂设不脱产卫生员呢？小厂可以设卫生员，大厂设医务所。","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"8fd9033d08","type":"paragraph","text":"答：非正式医生开不了假条，要请假还要到医院去，经医生开证明才行。","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"c871c6a2f2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这涉及到劳保问题，要好好考虑。","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"ab4632938c","type":"paragraph","text":"答：城市医院压力很大，公费医疗包下来，一个钱不出，到处看病。","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"e96fa316bd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：看了病，拿了药还不吃。","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"8a8fef01b3","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：总理指示城市要组织医务人员下农村，每年去三分之一。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"65405d7be5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：怎么下去，多久？","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"f1454b9ac5","type":"paragraph","text":"答：轮流下去。下去后城市医疗卫生工作仍比较重。我们打算高等医学院校学生三年就一边工作一边上课。护士也一面工作一面学习。","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"d3b16969dc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：光念念书是不行的。你们对打仗考虑了没有？","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"a7243c9f7f","type":"paragraph","text":"答：中央指示后考虑的。","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"ff794ad981","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：怎么考虑的。","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"e38e43fc67","type":"paragraph","text":"答：组织了××个医疗队，随时准备赴前线服务。现在的医院对战争没有训练。组织医疗队训练，有的地方已开始了。","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"f7d1fd3049","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：打仗了还能都到北京医院看病？要考虑到打仗。你们分科那么细，打起仗来怎么办？打起仗来还不是什么都要看，只会内科不会外科怎么行？","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"3505ff66fc","type":"paragraph","text":"答：过去部队年轻人多，疑难病可能不多，有的也许不认识。但是医学科学是发展的，要有一小部分力量搞尖端。","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"a6b02d71c7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：搞科研的人看不看病？","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"21131c0e98","type":"paragraph","text":"答：一部分人看病，一部分人不看病。","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"f02f537592","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：什么人不看病。","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"a6ccd6b4ed","type":"paragraph","text":"答：搞基础科学的，如搞生理、药理、生化的，研究理论不看病。","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"700f151371","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：理论还是要结合实际啊！","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"4a1d9cddfc","type":"paragraph","text":"答：×××同志说百分之五搞尖端就可以了，现在共有科研队伍××人，其中技术队伍××人。","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"61a74b6c72","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：科学尖端还是要搞的。","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"b1ab97187d","type":"paragraph","text":"请示：第一，卫生员的工分问题。人民公社六十条规定，补贴工分不超过百分之二，卫生员的补贴工分社员同意给，但六十条没有规定。","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"d5af48c028","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：给群众办好事没问题，农民会同意的。现在干部参加了劳动，百分之二也用不了，有的地方只用百分之一。工分不成问题，农民会同意的。","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"e89090a7ed","type":"paragraph","text":"请示：第二个问题，希望党委多领导、批评我们，多抓卫生工作。我们认识到党委多抓、多领导、批评，工作才有劲。","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"e2d132a154","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这话很对。党委是集体领导，什么都要管。卫生部门是为人民服务的，当然要抓，党委也要研究卫生工作。","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"ad3d86f2e0","type":"paragraph","text":"最近政治局不是要讨论卫生工作吗？你们的报告写得怎么样了？写好，送政治局。","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"e27462f895","type":"paragraph","text":"请示：农村卫生工作是个很重要的问题，建议中央今年召开一个农村卫生工作会议，中央召开可以找省市领导同志参加。","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"de0a926832","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：可以。","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"154425a561","type":"paragraph","text":"请示：还有有关药的问题。","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"49bff0545c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：药的问题怎么样？","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"441a6756df","type":"paragraph","text":"答：药不归卫生部门管，问题不少，现在正在研究解决。","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"e1e1dcc700","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：药品应当降价。","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"6c0bd14af8","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：药品降价对农民有一定的好处。但药主要用在城市，药降价，农民还是看不起病。","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"bed2afef35","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：天津计划生育不要钱。看来国家出了钱，实际是划得来的。国家出点钱保护生产力是合算的，药钱拿不起也可以不拿。你们开展农村卫生工作后，要搞节制生育。","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"5473cd881f","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我们医疗队下去也搞计划生育。","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"7db2a94048","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：农民接受得如何？","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"f15053cbe7","type":"paragraph","text":"答：宣传后可以接受。","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"a19789a5af","type":"paragraph","text":"最后，请示主席还有什么指示。","index":91,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"},{"id":"9ff21f8e67","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：没有什么了，就按你们讲的办吧！","index":92,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759"}],"page":{"id":"1c4c5f5a3e","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6fdd6a4759","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}